{"tid":1670336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁堅持要搞加泰集會而唔係聲援新疆","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T16:13:51.000Z","uid":58785,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4079214f497b6ecc64d1da8bd4781c6a0857e8f6","tid":1670336,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"有好多個post都有講點解反對搞加泰集會<br />\n簡單啲講就係加泰涉及獨立 <br />\n政治問題複雜好多 同時爭議性都大好多<br />\n最重要係好有可能會影響到國際支持香港嘅聲音<br />\n雖然劉穎匡話只係想提供個平台俾香港人瞭解加泰<br />\n但都好容易俾位對家入 連Solomon同Reddit啲人都開到聲唔好搞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家真係唔好去加泰集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n雖然我唔建議香港人喺自己都未顧掂自己仲去顧其他人<br />\n但如果左膠真係要咁大愛要搞集會<br />\n所謂敵人嘅敵人就係朋友 點解唔聲援新疆<br />\n新疆人權問題美國都成日批評 <br />\n國會甚至仲過埋新疆人權法<br />\n最重要係有共同敵人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中共</strong></span></span><br />\n咁個focus可以放喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>反中共極權</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我重申我立場係顧好香港先搞其他野 但如果左膠要搞 唔該就搞返反中共極權嘅野</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c075ef3a8b9cb5a6df4d25c079db737cde96e30","tid":1670336,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:19:01.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"b2bbcf07e12e6efc819d1a989e6931df7a2e031f","tid":1670336,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"d1f66ad2b7c734891ba6efffb510c3da22fd3b58","tid":1670336,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"45611f3c770c174f2fb2b8f0059263aa07bad719","tid":1670336,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"加泰post各位冷處理，不推文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bqn2BS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https