<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=e0ebe635\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=8af58553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"cfbe761f98ab556ce1cef9ee41f06dbf8aa56d87","tid":1670336,"uid":234089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"支持參加加泰獨立集會<br />\n一定要香港人奶一獲廿既 <br />\n諗起齊齊仆街 幾咁開心"},{"pid":"542cd998cb5802bb0df2273293aacc0221062b5f","tid":1670336,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"f6eec492632033f6d424838ee34932b04fba02bc","tid":1670336,"uid":189404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99dd1042537422c9046e7f99b23180032e08c616","tid":1670336,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"41e7b3c3af2aef8d380a689793bceac0a072f236","tid":1670336,"uid":189